{
  "stem": "5471.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very sad.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My husband never was home during the night before the transport-- always trying to figure out who went on transport.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Were people going from his office?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If they were, he tried to get them out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he was never home that night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But sometimes, someone came inside to say goodbye to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We never closed the door, not while we were living amongst the Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't have to be afraid for them, and the Germans didn't come there at night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I would be asleep, and I heard a knock on the bedroom door.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And someone came in to say goodbye.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a loss.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We tried so hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then you felt yourself a failure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Someone had to go again, and you couldn't prevent it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was always hopeless.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, say at about 8 o'clock, you saw all those people going past.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When we were living inside the camp, they walk-- pass our bedrooms' windows.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the cattle wagons were in front of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you saw all those people pushed in the doors-- and old folk, people on [NON-ENGLISH]--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--little kids.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What do you call it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stretchers-- brought to the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there the Germans were walking past, looking very self-proud, happy with themselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Another train was going, and Berlin had asked them, for instance, for 1,000 people, and they make sure the 1,000 were there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we tried to make sure that not 1,000, about a few less were going into there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my husband even once took a boy away who was inside the train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That boy cried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And still, later on, he went, only around the court.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That sounds strange.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I had, for instance, a girl working inside the house with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
